{"id": 1220, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在购买运动装备时都有什么困扰？", "description": "快来拯救一下只会穿老头汗衫的我！（题图来自：Patrick Leger）", "record_count": 2091, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160914152358r7L8Xenv5H9faxwR.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-16T17:00:28Z", "options": [{"id": 116992, "content": "运动衣越买越多，去健身房的时间越来越少", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760888}, {"id": 117248, "content": "是否对运动有促进作用…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 696748}, {"id": 116993, "content": "一入球鞋，中毒太深。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147030}, {"id": 117249, "content": "球鞋情节", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 365127}, {"id": 116994, "content": "基本上各种比较，挑最好的。最后用不了几次", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752865}, {"id": 116995, "content": "只穿老头衫运动的人可能有四个原因：运动量不够汗不多，没体会过排汗服的好处，没身材，没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 312466}, {"id": 116997, "content": "骚绿和骚蓝会十分亮眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737312}, {"id": 117253, "content": "胖子怎么买运动服……都显得好紧……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761837}, {"id": 117254, "content": "会不会激凸", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735337}, {"id": 116999, "content": "外观与价格  而且 不运动", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 210140}, {"id": 117000, "content": "选专业性强的还是时尚帅气的，还有考虑性价比", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760899}, {"id": 117256, "content": "衣服，鞋子，耳机，少了一样都不能好好运动。最重要的是心情，身边却总是有些人喜欢你按他们的方式去运动，我又不跟你一起，管好自己得了。毛病不是一点点！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649788}, {"id": 117001, "content": "为了突出运动风，设计师的设计在大多数情况下都除斥着亮色，不喜欢没关系，反正你也没得选不是？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346569}, {"id": 117258, "content": "还要费脑子去买能配套的衣服和裤子?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 756520}, {"id": 119562, "content": "穿什么都丑?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773552}, {"id": 117259, "content": "学生党啊，最主要的还是money噻 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761856}, {"id": 117262, "content": "穿模特儿身上很帅，穿自己身上很挫。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484031}, {"id": 117263, "content": "贵~", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 753771}, {"id": 117264, "content": "运动内衣纠结s还是m，m好像有些轻松，s好像又有些紧。摊手！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741203}, {"id": 117009, "content": "为自己用不着的功能困扰：其实自己不专业，却非要挑很专业的装备。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673174}, {"id": 117012, "content": "bra穿着太紧，不紧跑起来又没什么卵用", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 551379}, {"id": 117268, "content": "其实不需要这些装备", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 756316}, {"id": 117269, "content": "问一群气质萎靡懒到发霉五短身材肥肚腩救生圈腰腹的死宅懒癌晚期矫情病重度患者买运动装备都遇到什么困难？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411792}, {"id": 117015, "content": "想买专业球鞋又苦于价格问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 760238}, {"id": 117271, "content": "其实真正的困扰是来自于自己不知道要干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668641}, {"id": 117016, "content": "尺码\n外观", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 748923}, {"id": 115739, "content": "网上买运动bra，比单纯买bra更难确定码数", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 117019, "content": "这么多的保护设备我到底要不要买 鸡肋还是鸡腿？", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 750539}, {"id": 115740, "content": "市面上的运动紧身弹力裤穿上总会有两条明显的内裤勒痕，尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 137, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 117020, "content": "钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635818}, {"id": 117276, "content": "搞不懂那些来健身出汗的人戴一棒球帽 赤裸裸的装?️", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761886}, {"id": 115741, "content": "不想买球星鞋，穿一双球星鞋结果打得特别烂会被嘲笑的", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 117021, "content": "衣服太丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690124}, {"id": 117277, "content": "健身要买训练鞋 别买跑步和篮球鞋 要不然别人会觉得你是来摆摆样子拍个照的 一定要买训练鞋 切记", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761886}, {"id": 115742, "content": "衣服鞋什么的大多数是很炫很Rihanna的颜色，性冷风啥时候刮到这个领域啊？", "image": null, "praise_count": 262, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 117022, "content": "自从买了跑鞋和运动手环，再也不跑步了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736242}, {"id": 117280, "content": "要凸显自己身材的，材质好的，摸着舒服的，牌子好的，好看的，低调有点小特别的。最重要还是便宜的??", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162702}, {"id": 117025, "content": "无底洞啊无底洞，装备要好，钱要舍得～", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589115}, {"id": 117281, "content": "钱啊啊啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712707}, {"id": 117026, "content": "肚子超过胸围，别穿紧身衣。压缩裤紧身裤别当外裤穿，腿部没肌肉，记得买小一码。UA基础系列是水泥性冷淡，NIKE联名系列是安德伍德伪冷淡。MMA的训练服是狂躁二次元。日系的，还停留在90年代奥运会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 438940}, {"id": 117027, "content": "要速干又要舒服和好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348081}, {"id": 117285, "content": "愚蠢和偏见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152727}, {"id": 117034, "content": "不要太骚 得体就好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698802}, {"id": 117291, "content": "我是挑颜色显眼的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761926}, {"id": 117037, "content": "xs号的运动裤一直都不好买", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 198685}, {"id": 117293, "content": "我是挑颜色显眼的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761926}, {"id": 117295, "content": "一运动就想买装备奖励自己。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274023}, {"id": 117041, "content": "价格", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692867}, {"id": 117043, "content": "若有长期跑步，强烈建议买一双好的护膝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 756652}, {"id": 117044, "content": "比一般的衣裤鞋贵好多", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610536}]}